description: People of the Chubbs is a gourmet street food experience unlike any other. Serving up such varied fare as burgers, rice plates, tacos, flautas, pizza rolls, and more, all with your choices of cilantro or sriracha garlic aolis or other sauces, this truck is sure to please anyone in pursuit of a good meal. Find the truck on the streets of Renton, and get yourself a taco or some poutine!
name: People of the Chubbs
